tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE third_party_services (
    service_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    service_name VARCHAR(255),
    api_endpoint VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE cloud_applications (
    app_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    app_name VARCHAR(255),
    app_description TEXT,
    app_owner VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE integration_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    service_id INT REFERENCES third_party_services(service_id),
    app_id INT REFERENCES cloud_applications(app_id),
    log_message TEXT,
    log_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE service_usage (
    usage_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    service_id INT REFERENCES third_party_services(service_id),
    usage_count INT,
    usage_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE third_party_services (
  service_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  service_name VARCHAR(255),
  api_key VARCHAR(50),
  integration_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE cloud_applications (
  app_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  app_name VARCHAR(255),
  app_type VARCHAR(50),
  app_owner VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE api_endpoints (
  endpoint_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  endpoint_url VARCHAR(255),
  endpoint_description TEXT,
  api_key_required BOOL
)

CREATE TABLE integration_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  integration_date DATETIME,
  integration_status VARCHAR(20),
  error_message TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE user_permissions (
  permission_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  endpoint_id INT,
  permission_level INT
)
